{"tid":1908060,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中共玩fake news, 就搞到班外國華僑搶日用品","createTime":"2020-03-03T04:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T04:55:00.000Z","uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a09076b483150a0fe9b5f273bd2257ade49bee3","tid":1908060,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"中共呢一招會唔會唔合乎logic?<br />\n一開始香港搶日用品, 係基於以下原因<br />\n1 支那封城, 無人番工<br />\n2 東亞病夫掛住病, 無人做野<br />\n3生產線斷<br />\n<br />\n但中共一邊吹復工風, 經濟向好<br />\n即係有人番工, 有人生產, 生產線&amp; supply chain 正常<br />\n<br />\n但中共另一個部門又一邊倒自己米<br />\nD海外統戰部又出fake news 呃外國華僑搶日用品<br />\n<br />\n點樣即係咩玩法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0705debb04675105aa6ed5c505ca29af109a2626","tid":1908060,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣<br />\n 點會係搶日用品<br />\n廁紙呢D賤種商品, 求其搵一班病君, 按個button 都大量生產啦<br />\n<br />\n怕供應鍊斷裂, 點都係怕大陸果班光學,電子零件斷好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840640cbe0470262ff515729734a13ae5cb11421","tid":1908060,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"中國歌舞昇平，外國水深火熱，做比大陸人睇"},{"pid":"ee228c00ebb16362cf31fa010d124465857a24fc","tid":1908060,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"840640cbe0470262ff515729734a13ae5cb11421","tid":1908060,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"中國歌舞昇平，外國水深火熱，做比大陸人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"e1feba14d2c909e3d4e3f6f1824362d8a9cb9feb","tid":1908060,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"840640cbe0470262ff515729734a13ae5cb11421","tid":1908060,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"中國歌舞昇平，外國水深火熱，做比大陸人睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202